| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5565 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 41d7ec25-2043-5a4f-bd2d-3c50dd9f8711"
